25 SECTION 1. Arkansas Code Title 18, Chapter 16, Subchapter 4, is
26 amended to add an additional section to read as follows:
27 18-16-416. Compromised leased space — Notification required —
28 Definitions.
29 (a) As used in this section:
30 (1) "Compromised" means that an operator has actual knowledge
31 that:
32 (A) A leased space has been forcibly accessed by an
33 individual other than the occupant, the operator, or an individual authorized
34 by the occupant or the operator;
35 (B) Property has been taken from a leased space by an
36 individual other than the occupant, the operator, or an individual authorized
